(6, 69, 'Ambi Pur Starter Pack Car AC Vent Air Freshener Perfume- Aqua', 354.015, 100, 'ambi-pur-aqua-ac-vent.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">A unique compact air freshener, specially designed for use with your car vent system. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">A watery citrus fragrance with some fresh spicy hints.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"> Inspired by the energetic walk over the mountains and the waterfalls filled with fog. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">Imagine you are standing before a waterfall covered with morning dew, a deep breath and feel the fresh air, pure as invigorating for you to start a new day full of excitement. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">With the clamp on the door of the air conditioner wind unique design can adjust the level to emit a scent that will help you control the amount of scent emitted over the vehicle and time using the product.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>LASTS UP TO 45 DAYS</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong> </strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;line-height:1.5em;">Begin your journey with the mesmerising and the best ever perfume set of Ambi Pur.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;line-height:1.5em;"> Just fix on the AC vent, turn the flow switch on the perfume kit and let the fragrance take your into a different world. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;line-height:1.5em;">Sit back, breathe in, and enjoy the ride. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;line-height:1.5em;">Keep your car smelling clean and fresh no matter the distance.</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"> <strong>Features :</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">-The fresh sensation of open air wherever you go.</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"> -Ambi pur Car provides you the right freshness with the intensity you choose</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"> -Fragrance- Aqua</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"> These unique fragrances will create an inviting atmosphere inside your home and car.</span></p>', '2016-05-27 16:05:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7, 109, 'Black Label Car Gel Freshener Perfume -Yellow Lemon Set of 2', 820, 10, 'black-label-car-gel-freshener-perfume-yellow-lemon-set-of-2.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>Description:</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">- Very different air freshener</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"> - Emits a refreshing and mild smell</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"> - The highest grade liquid perfuming agent packed in an aromatic master piece</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"> - Eradicates foul odours makes the environment a better place to live and work in. </span></p>\n<p> </p>', '2016-05-27 16:05:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
