(37, 109, 'LA AROMA - Car Air Freshener - Refreshing Lime - 80 gms', 225, 22, 'la-aroma-car-air-freshener-refreshing-lime-80-gms.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">Introducing new car fresheners from LA AROMA at affordable prices.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">La Aroma Lime scent is useful to those living in highly industrialized areas in India. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">In these localities, the high intensity dust emitted from industries can pass through car interiors and will generate an undesirable odor, lime flavor emitted from La Aroma, will transform an unfavorable odor into a most pleasant one.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">Car perfumes La Aroma lime makes the entire car ride experience a pleasurable one, especially during a hot sunny afternoon. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">There are many take away eatery joints in India, people can enjoy eating a delicious meal or ice cream in cars to greater levels when surrounded by the pleasant odor of La Aroma Lime scent, without this the experience is pretty claustrophobic.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">La Aroma lime scent is appreciated for its pleasant odor, the combination of your car and La Aroma perfume is amazing. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">The Lime perfume is an excellent tool to experience an amazing interior car odor when sweating profusely.</span><br /></p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>Quantity : 80 gms</strong></span></p>\n<p></p>', '2016-05-27 16:05:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
