(57, 107, 'Mothers - Glass cleaner - 710 ml', 890, 49, 'mothers-glass-cleaner-710-ml.jpg', '<p>Road film, oily deposits and grime don’t stand a chance against Mothers® Glass Cleaner. Great on all automotive glass, headlight lenses, mirrors and even chrome, this glass cleaner doesn’t leave streaks. Our professional strength formula is safe and ammonia-free, so it won’t harm your tinted window film.</p>', '2016-05-27 16:05:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
