(136, 69, 'Meguiars Gold Class Applicator Pad(Pack Of 4)', 522, 37, 'meguiar-s-gold-class-applicator-padpack-of-4.jpg', '<p>CLEAR COAT SAFE Meguiar''s Foam Applicator Pad (4) 4.5 inch reusable pads in a convenient polybag. For use on paint, Wheels, Tyres, &amp; Windows Non scratching tight celled foam safe even application of Polishes &amp; Waxes Re-usable &amp; machine washable</p>', '2016-05-27 16:05:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
