To Office/ Go Home</span></div>\n<div style="padding:5px;"><span style="font-size:10pt;">Going to office and home will be much easier. No more complicated search. With a simple click, Garmin device guides you to office or home.</span></div>\n</td>\n</tr></tbody></table><p></p>', '2016-05-27 16:05:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(159, 137, 'Garmin GPS Navigator - Nuvi ® 2568LM (India)', 17990, 50, 'garmin-gps-navigator-nuvi-2568lm-india.jpg', '<h3> </h3>\n<h3><span style="font-size:10pt;"><strong>Advanced Series Navigation for Your Car</strong></span></h3>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li><span style="font-size:10pt;">12.7cm display</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size:10pt;">Brand new user interface</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size:10pt;">Detailed maps of India with free lifetime¹ updates</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size:10pt;">Garmin photoReal Junction View</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size:10pt;">Preloaded with Travel Guide</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size:10pt;">Bluetooth compatible</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size:10pt;">Driving Recorder compatible</span></li>\n</ul><p> </p>\n<h3><span style="font-size:10pt;"><strong>Bright Display</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">nüvi 2568LM has a bright 12.7cm display.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><span style="font-size:10pt;"><strong>Brand New User Interface</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">An advanced navigation engineproviding a faster, more intuitive user interfaceto enhance the speed, convenience andaccuracy of searches and routing for everydaydriving.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><span style="font-size:10pt;"><strong>Detailed Maps with Free Updates</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">nüvi 2568LM arrives loaded with detailed maps of India. With free lifetime¹ map updates, your routes are sure to reflect the most up-to-date maps, POIs (points of interest) and navigation information. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">New maps are available for download up to 4 times per year, for the life of your device, with no fees.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">With so much data, nüvi 2568LM makes it easy to find addresses and 7.3 millions of POIs such as shops, restaurants and other destinations. nüvi 2568LM arrives preloaded with POIs, so there’s no need for you to enter that address information. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">Just select one — or many — and navigate there, quickly and easily. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">You also have the ability to add custom POIs to your nüvi 2568LM.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><span style="font-size:10pt;"><strong>Garmin photoReal Junction View</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">No more guessing which lane you need to be in to make an upcoming turn. photoReal junction view realistically displays junctions and interchanges along your route, including the surrounding landscape. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">Brightly colored arrows indicate the proper lane to drive. nüvi 2568LM also depicts real road signs as they appear along your route.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><span style="font-size:10pt;"><strong>More Information at a Glance</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">nüvi 2568LM keeps your driving map onscreen at all times and additional information appears alongside. For details, simply ask or touch the screen. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">As you drive your route, Up ahead constantly informs you of nearby services, including restaurants, fuel stations, hospitals and stores. nüvi 2568LM displays speed limit, current speed and accurate time of arrival. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">With a quick glance, you can read the name of your current street. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">Plus, you’ll be surprised to see Point Of Interest icons on the maps and no need to page through menus. Have you ever had trouble finding the parking around you? </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">Garmin brand new user interface will automatically provide parking information near your destination.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><span style="font-size:10pt;"><strong>Travel Guide </strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">Plan your trip and travel with your Garmin navigator without the burden of travel books! Garmin Travel Guide now available in India, bringing you in-depth coverage of long standing historical monuments, and fine dining places.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><span style="font-size:10pt;"><strong>Bluetooth® Compatible</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">Sync a Bluetooth-enabled device, such as your smartphone, to nüvi 2568LM for hands-free calling through its integrated microphone and speaker. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">Safely stow your phone in a glove compartment, pocket or purse and still make and take calls without moving your hands from the steering wheel or your eyes from the road.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><span style="font-size:10pt;"><strong>Driving Recorder Compatible</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style="font-size:10pt;">Garmin GDR30 with 1080p Full-HD quality provides you a much safer driving experience. To record any traffic or accident, even scenery and edit video by yourself.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5"><tbody><tr><td colspan="2" bgcolor="#ccddfc">\n<h3><span style="font-size:10pt;"><strong>Specifications</strong></span></h3>\n</td>\n</tr><tr bgcolor="#edf3fe"><td><span style="font-size:10pt;">Display size</span></td>\n<td><span style="font-size:10pt;">12.7cm diag</span></td>\n</tr><tr><td><span style="font-size:10pt;">Display resolution</span></td>\n<td><span style="font-size:10pt;">480x272 pixels</span></td>\n</tr><tr bgcolor="#edf3fe"><td><span style="font-size:10pt;">Battery </span></td>\n<td><span style="font-size:10pt;">rechargeable lithium-ion </span></td>\n</tr><tr><td><span style="font-size:10pt;">Battery life</span></td>\n<td><span style="font-size:10pt;">Up to 2.5 hrs</span></td>\n</tr><tr bgcolor="#edf3fe"><td><span style="font-size:10pt;">High-sensitiviy receiver</span></td>\n<td><span style="font-size:10pt