(376, 151, '3M Engine Oil Additive', 587, 10, '3m-engine-oil-additive.jpg', '<p><strong>3M™ Engine Oil Additive</strong><br />For professional use only<br />     - Reduces friction of critical engine parts for petrol &amp; diesel engines<br />     - Helps improve engine power and performance<br />     - Helps stop oil foaming for better lubrication<br />     - Protects against oil film break down<br />     - Reduces build up of harmful deposits<br />     - Compatible with all types of motor oil<br />     - Helps improve life of engine components</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>Directions For Use</strong><br />     - Recommended for vehicles up to 50,000 Kms<br />     - With engine off, add 3M™ Engine Oil Additive to crankcase along with new engine oil.<br />     - For best results, add during every oil change.<br />     - Treat Rate: 250 ml for engines with oil capacities of 3 to 5 litres (Typically engines with 2.5 litre displacement or less)<br />     - Use full content for one engine<br />     - Do not overfill oil. If necessary, reduce the amount of added oil to the crankcase<br />     - Check the oil level-Add or remove oil as necessary.?</p>', '2016-05-27 16:29:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
