(387, 69, 'Osram H4 COOL BLUE INTENSE XENON LOOK 12V 60/55W', 1025, 47, 'osram-h4-cool-blue-intense-xenon-look-12v-60-55w.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>Product Description</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li><span style="font-size:12pt;">Xenon effect</span></li>\n<li></li>\n<li><span style="font-size:12pt;">Product made in Germany</span></li>\n<li></li>\n<li><span style="font-size:12pt;">Fully road legal within the EU</span></li>\n<li></li>\n<li><span style="font-size:12pt;">For the design-conscious driver</span></li>\n<li></li>\n<li><span style="font-size:12pt;">Modern, bright bluish-white light</span></li>\n<li></li>\n<li><span style="font-size:12pt;">Up to 20% more light on the road</span></li>\n<li></li>\n<li><span style="font-size:12pt;">High-contrast illumination of the road</span></li>\n</ul><p> </p>', '2016-05-27 16:29:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(388, 165, 'Osram LEDriving Daytime Running Lights (DRL)12V', 7750, 50, 'osram-ledriving-daytime-running-lights-drl12v.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">OSRAM :  Introduces their latest daytime running light (DRL) kit - OSRAM LEDriving®.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"> With a colour temperature of 5200K, it''s the perfect styling addition to your vehicle.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>Key features:</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    Suitable for Daytime Running Light application</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    ECE R87 SAE IP67 approved</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    5 dotted LED effect</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    Comprehensive fitting instructions included in every box</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    Approx. 2 hour fitting time</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>The kit includes:</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    x 2 LEDriving Modules</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    x 2 mounting brackets</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    x 1 control module</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    x 1 cable connector</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    x 6 screws</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    x 10 cable ties</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>Each unit has the following dimensions:</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    160 mm wide</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    23 mm high</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    30 mm deep</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"><img src="http://www.autobulbsdirect.co.uk/images/D/lights-on.jpg" alt="" width="750" height="453" /></span></p>', '2016-05-27 16:29:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(389, 165, 'OSRAM LED Light@Day Daytime Running Light Kit (DRL)', 10100, 48, 'osram-led-lightday-daytime-running-light-kit-drl.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">OSRAM introduce a new product to their range of leading automotive products. The OSRAM LED Light@Day daytime running light kit provides you with with a simple and affordable way to add LED styling to your existing vehicle.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>What makes it different?</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Instead of having a series of individual LEDs, the OSRAM LED Light@Day daytime running light kit has a single continous beam of light - a sweeping style light - for a unified and stylish effect.</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>Technology, styling and energy efficiency combined</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">The innovative design features the latest high performance LEDs with light guide technology, ensuring the best possible visibility with very low additional fuel consumption - just 0.02 litres per 100 kilometres. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">This is certainly likely to be lower than if you were to drive through the day with low/dipped beam bulbs on.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">The result of installing OSRAM LED Light@Day is an improvement in safety and styling. The kit can be easily installed and is safe to use in automatic car washes.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>Each unit has the following dimensions:</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    167 mm wide</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    31.2 mm high</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    46.9 mm deep</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>Information:-</strong></span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">LED Light@Day: Stylish daytime running lights</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>Product benefits</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    Homogenous light, without light points</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    Low energy consumption</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    Intensive carwashes possible thanks to high protection class (IP69K)</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    Easy installation</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    Suitable for many vehicle models</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>Product features</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    Retrofit LED daytime running light</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    Eye-catching design and sweeping lines for a dynamic look</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">    Color temperature: up to 6,000 K</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">With the Osram LED Light@Day daytime running light kit, the lighting manufacturer has launched a retrofit LED daytime running light with a homogenous light area which uses light guide technology and therefore reduces visible LED points. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">The high-performance LEDs ensure optimal visibility during the day and, being so efficient, increase fuel consumption by only 0.02 litres per 100 kilometres.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"> These ECE (Economic Commission for Europe)-approved daytime running lights are characterised by their modern and curved design, granting the vehicle a dynamic appearance. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">They are suitable for many makes and models of vehicles, and can be installed by oneself easily. Due to its IP 69K protection class intensive car washes pose no problem for the LED Light@Day. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">Optionally, the daytime running light can also be used as navigation light.</span></p>', '2016-05-27 16:29:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
