(395, 165, 'Osram H4 / DH4 Xenon 35W 6000K Conversion Kit', 9520, 50, 'osram-h4-dh4-xenon-35w-6000k-conversion-kit.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Features</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">• 35 Watts</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">• Rigorous Testing</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">• Protections the Environment</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">• Higher Colour than Ordinary Halogen Light Colour</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">• Cost-Efficient</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">The Osram DH1 6000K HID KIT 35W ensures you travel safely, especially at night time. The Osram retrofit kit has gone through rigorous testing as per industry reliability test requirements including waterproof, high temperature and seismic tests. </span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">When you have the Osram DH1 6000K HID KIT installed in your car, you can safely travel at night as it has a higher colour temperature than halogen light colour. </span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">It reduces visual tiredness as the colour is of more bluish white, closer to the natural light colour, thereby letting you drive with no fear. </span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">It protects the environment as it lowers the influence on the environment and thereby conserves the natural resources. You can also intensify the brightness of the lights and is more energy efficient. </span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">The kit is cost-efficient as has long life service, thanks to high reliability. It decreases replacement frequency and maintenance costs.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Specifications</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">GENERAL</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Brand Osram</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Product Model H4</span><br /><span s