(396, 165, 'Osram H7 Xenon H7 35W 6000K H7 Conversion Kit', 8750, 49, 'osram-h7-xenon-h7-35w-6000k-h7-conversion-kit.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Lighting Techniks 35W 6000K H7 HID Conversion Kit w/ Digital Slim Ballast, by OptiksHID </span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Our HID Conversion Kit''s have been engineered utilizing German Ballast Technology. As automobile enthusiast ourselves, we understand the importance of a high quality yet cost effective HID Conversion Kit. </span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">HID Xenon systems not only produce 3 times the amount light than a standard halogen bulb, it actually uses less power.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Our German Ballast Technology uses integrated digital current regulators to monitor and control the electric current to the HID bulbs. This ensures NO flicker while also prolonging the lifespan of the bulb. </span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Each HID Conversion Kit contains the following:</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">    2x Digital Slim Ballast (1 Pair)</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">    2x HID Xenon Light Bulbs (1 Pair)</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">    Mounting Hardware for Digital Slim Ballast</span><br /><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>**Attention:</strong>  HID Conversion Kit''s are for Off-Road Use ONLY.  Please consult your individual state regulation''s regarding the use of HID Xenon Lighting Systems.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Features:</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">    Better Visibility (3x lumens compared to standard halogen)</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">    Longer Life (rated at 4000 hours)</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">    Less Power Consumption (only 35W)</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">    Digital Slim 