(555, 150, 'Bosch Cabin Filter For Maruti Swift / Ertiga / Dzire / SX4 (D/P) - Activated', 1330, 47, 'bosch-cabin-filter-for-maruti-swift-ertiga-dzire-sx4-d-p-activated.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">Bosch activated carbon cabin filters even filtrate odors!</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">An Activated Carbon Cabin Filter from Bosch can do everything, what a Standard Cabin Filter* can do – and more.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Even fumes are withheld by Cabin Filters with an activated carbon layer. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">The structure of this special carbon has very fine pores and captures gases perfectly.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Now you can keep your air conditioner and blower fan turned on during traffic jams, while driv-ing through tunnels or the countryside. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">Unpleasant odors are reduced noticeably. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">But also odor-less gases, such as ozone, are withheld in the activated carbon layer.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">For a safer and healthier driving condition, trust Bosch, the worldwide filter specialist.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">* You can see everything a Bosch standard cabin filter does in the section “Standard cabin filter”.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">A fresh Bosch cabin filter is good for your health.</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">And your air conditioning will also be happy about a filter replacement. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">It will be more efficient and help save fuel.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">When to replace?</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Cabin filters should be replaced every 15,000 km or according to the vehicle manufacturer specifications. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">You will also feel it when it''s time to replace the filter:</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">- The windows steam up more quickly.</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">- More dust gathers inside the vehicle.</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">- The air smells bad.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Which filter is the right one?</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">All Bosch filters have original equipment quality. To ensure you are using the correct filter for your vehicle, note the following aspects* before purchasing a Bosch cabin filter:</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">- Vehicle model.</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">- Year of manufacture of the vehicle.</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">- Vehicle with or without air conditioning.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">* You can find this information on every DIY packaging of Bosch cabin filters.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Standard or activated carbon?</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">You are not sure whether a filter with or without activated carbon is the right one for you? Our product information will help you decide:</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">- Standard cabin filter.</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">- Activated carbon cabin filter.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">How to replace?</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Detailed installation instructions come with all Bosch cabin filters. Please dispose of your old cabin filter in the domestic waste.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">For a safer and healthier driving condition, trust Bosch, the worldwide filter specialist.?</span></p>', '2016-05-27 16:34:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
