(567, 150, 'Bosch Cabin Filter For Maruti Swift / Ertiga / Dzire / SX4 (D/P) - Standard', 717, 47, 'bosch-cabin-filter-for-maruti-swift-ertiga-dzire-sx4-d-p-standard.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">Bosch Cabin Filter For Maruti Swift / Ertiga / Dzire / SX4 (D/P) - Standard</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">A fresh Bosch cabin filter is good for your health.</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">And your air conditioning will also be happy about a filter replacement. It will be more efficient and help save fuel.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">When to replace?</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Cabin filters should be replaced every 15,000 km or according to the vehicle manufacturer specifications. You will also feel it when it''s time to replace the filter:</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">- The windows steam up more quickly.</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">- More dust gathers inside the vehicle.</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">- The air smells bad.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Which filter is the right one?</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">All Bosch filters have original equipment quality. To ensure you are using the correct filter for your vehicle, note the following aspects* before purchasing a Bosch cabin filter:</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">- Vehicle model.</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">- Year of manufacture of the vehicle.</span><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">- Vehicle with or without air conditioning.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">* You can find this information on every DIY packaging of Bosch cabin filters.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Standard or activated carbon?</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">You are not sure whether a filter with or without activated carbon is the right one for you? Our product information will help you decide:</span><br 