(610, 69, 'Worldtech Door/ Rear Deck Speakers 800W-3 Way 3 Speakers', 2500, 100, 'gto-949-6-x-9-3-way-speakers-400w.jpg', '<p><strong>Description</strong></p>\n<p><br /> 800w MAX POWER.<br /> 4 Way coaxial speaker.<br /> Impedance 4 Ohm.<br /> Frequency Response 45-20KHz.<br /> Sensitivity 90.3dB (1m)<br /> Output Power RMS 100Watts<br /> Mylar + Piezo Tweete</p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(611, 131, 'CS-4 4 Co Axial 2 Way Speakers', 1690, 10, 'cs-4-4-co-axial-2-way-speakers.jpg', 'Powerful, advanced multielement and component speakers to upgrade any car audio system. - Upgrading your speakers is a great way to add real muscle to your car audio system, and JBL® CS Series multielement and component speakers have muscle to spare.1. Vented motor assemblies dissipate heat effectively to play louder without power compression,2. Separate woofer and tweeter modules with external crossover for improved response (CS-6Cand CS-5C only),3. 3-way design improves high-frequency response (CS-69 only)', '2016-05-27 16:35:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(612, 131, 'CS-5 5 1/4 Co Axial 2 Way Speakers', 1990, 10, 'cs-5-5-1-4-co-axial-2-way-speakers.jpg', 'Upgrading your speakers is a great way to add real muscle to your car audio system, and JBL® CS Series multielement and component speakers have muscle to spare.1. Vented motor assemblies dissipate heat effectively to play louder without power compression,2. Separate woofer and tweeter modules with external crossover for improved response(CS-6C and CS-5C only),3. 3-way design improves high-frequency response (CS-69 only),4.Available in the most popular hole sizes and configurations, CS Series speakers are designed to fit neatly into almost all factory speaker locations and feature advanced materials and technologies that endow them with exceptional performance characteristics,5.If it’s bass you’re interested in, proprietary CS woofer cones incorporating our patentedPlus One® technology deliver more of it than competitive cones of the same size,6.If it’s heat you’re worried about, CS motor structures dissipate it more effectively than conventional motor assemblies, enabling CS systems to play loud and long in the performance-proven JBL tradition,7.With 4-ohm designs and peak power ratings of 90 to 210 watts, CS Series speakerscan be safely driven by any factory head unit – but thankfully with no resemblance to factory sound.', '2016-05-27 16:35:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(613, 131, 'CS-6 6.5 Co Axial 2 Way Speakers', 2990, 10, 'cs-6-65-co-axial-2-way-speakers.jpg', 'Powerful, advanced multielement and component speakers to upgrade any car audio system. - Upgrading your speakers is a great way to add real muscle to your car audio system, and JBL® CS Series multielement and component speakers have muscle to spare.1. Vented motor assemblies dissipate heat effectively to play louder without power compression,2. Separate woofer and tweeter modules with external crossover for improved response (CS-6Cand CS-5C only),3.3-way design improves high-frequency response (CS-69 only)', '2016-05-27 16:35:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(614, 131, 'CS-5C 5 1/4 Component system', 5490, 10, 'cs-5c-5-1-4-component-system.jpg', 'Upgrading your speakers is a great way to add real muscle to your car audio system, and JBL® CS Series multielement and component speakers have muscle to spare. Available in the most popular hole sizes and configurations, CS Series speakers are designed to fit neatly into almost all factory speaker locations and feature advanced materials and technologies that endow them with exceptional performance characteristics. If it’s bass you’re interested in, proprietary CS woofer cones incorporating our patented Plus One® technology deliver more of it than competitive cones of the same size. If it’s heat you’re worried about, CS motor structures dissipate it more effectively than conventional motor assemblies, enabling CS systems to play loud and long in the performance-proven JBL tradition. With 4-ohm designs and peak power ratings of 90 to 210 watts, CS Series speakers can be safely driven by any factory head unit – but thankfully with no resemblance to factory sound.', '2016-05-27 16:35:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(615, 131, 'CS-6C 6.5 Components 260W', 5990, 10, 'cs-6c-65-components-260w.jpg', 'Powerful, advanced multielement and component speakers to upgrade any car audio system. - Upgrading your speakers is a great way to add real muscle to your car audio system, and JBL® CS Series multielement and component speakers have muscle to spare.1. Vented motor assemblies dissipate heat effectively to play louder without power compression,2. Separate woofer and tweeter modules with external crossover for improved response (CS-6Cand CS-5C only),3.3-way design improves high-frequency response (CS-69 only)', '2016-05-27 16:35:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
