(625, 134, 'Rockford Fosgate Punch P500-1bd Mono Amplifier', 26350, 10, 'rockford-fosgate-punch-p500-1bd-mono-amplifier.jpg', 'The Punch P500-1bd is a mono amplifier capable of 500 Watts into a 1-Ohm load. The Class-BD technology produces bass more efficiently over traditional amps, and its frequency response allows it to be optimized for subwoofers.1.12dB/octave crossover,2.MOSFET power supply,3.MOSFET output stage,4.4 Gauge power/ground terminals,5.Audiophile grade speaker connections,6.Top Mounted LED Indicators,7.RCA pass-thru,8.Infrasonic filter,9.1 Year Standard Warranty', '2016-05-27 16:35:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(626, 133, 'ROCKFORD FOSGATE P3L-S10 P3 SHALLOW SERIES 10 inches SUBWOOFER', 16990, 10, 'rockford-fosgate-p3l-s10-p3-shallow-series-10-subwoofer.jpg', '<p>The P3L-S10 is a single 10” shallow enclosure with 300 Watts RMS power handling wired to a 4-Ohm load. The enclosure is constructed with 5/8” MDF, covered in high density carpet, and features quick release compression terminals.1.Computer optimized design,2.Constructed with 1/2" MDF,3.Covered with high density carpet,4.High current binding posts,5.Wired exclusively with Rockford Fosgate speaker cable,6.1 Year Standard Warranty</p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(627, 133, 'ROCKFORD FOSGATE P1S410 PUNCH - P1-10 SUBWOOFER', 5990, 10, 'rockford-fosgate-p1s410-punch-p1-10-subwoofer.jpg', 'The P1 10" subwoofers are a great choice for those looking to add some PUNCH to their system without breaking the bank. They are designed for small enclosures, so they won''''t monopolize your trunk space either.', '2016-05-27 16:35:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(628, 133, 'ROCKFORD FOSGATE R1L-1X12 PASSIVE SERIES 12 SUBWOOFER', 9990, 10, 'rockford-fosgate-r1l-1x12-passive-series-12-subwoofer.jpg', 'Need Rockford Fosgate bass in a hurry? Drop this single 12" Prime Loaded enclosure in your ride and let the tunes bump! Featuring high current binding posts, 5/8" MDF construction and finished with high density carpet, these loaded enclosures will produce enough bass to make your friends say "Boom Yeah - Rockford Fosgate!"', '2016-05-27 16:35:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(629, 133, 'ROCKFORD FOSGATE R1L-2X12 PASSIVE SERIES 12 SUBWOOFER', 16490, 10, 'rockford-fosgate-r1l-2x12-passive-series-12-subwoofer.jpg', 'Rockford Fosgate''s Prime Series loaded sub enclosures let you put big bass in your car without taking a big hit to your bank account. These tough-as-nails sealed boxes feature 5/8"-thick medium-density fiberboard construction and heavy-duty black carpeting for protection. Rockford Fosgate used their Loudspeaker Enclosure Analysis Program to create an enclosure that''ll draw every ounce of bass out of its two subs.The R1L-2X12 sealed loaded enclosure comes with two Prime 4-ohm 12" subs, and handles up to 300 watts RMS. Each Prime sub features a polypropylene cone and butyl rubber surround, and the subs are matched to the enclosure for accurate bass that just won''t quit.', '2016-05-27 16:35:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(630, 133, 'ROCKFORD FOSGATE P1L-1X12 P1 SERIES 12 SUBWOOFER', 17990, 10, 'rockford-fosgate-p1l-1x12-p1-series-12-subwoofer.jpg', 'The most convenient way to get low frequency bass in your system is to drop-in a Punch Loaded enclosure. We''re not talking junk in the trunk, we''re talking the same genuine Punch woofers available seperately. Punch Loaded enclosures are constructed with durable 5/8" MDF and tuned by our computer aided design software. P1 Loaded Enclosures feature similar tonal performance as P2 &amp; P3 models, but are easier to move in-n-out of vehicles due to their lighter weight.', '2016-05-27 16:35:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(631, 133, 'ROCKFORD FOSGATE P2L-2X12 P2 SERIES 12 SUBWOOFER', 29900, 10, 'rockford-fosgate-p2l-2x12-p2-series-12-subwoofer.jpg', 'A great looking compact enclosure that will not leave you strapped for cash! The P2L-2X12 features two genuine P2D412 Punch woofers, an updated high-flow, low-noise port design, solid 5/8" MDF construction and 10AWG input terminals for the fantastic sound you expect from Rockford Fosgate.', '2016-05-27 16:35:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(632, 133, 'ROCKFORD FOSGATE T2D212 POWER - T2 12 SUBWOOFER', 54990, 10, 'rockford-fosgate-t2d212-power-t2-12-subwoofer.jpg', 'The upgraded Power T2D212 subwoofer has a new bad-ass look having revised components over the previous model. The T2 12” features dual 2-Ohm voice coils, 1,200 Watts RMS power handling, and includes an aluminum trim ring. 1.Rigid die-cast aluminum basket,2.Precision cast aluminum alloy basket,3.High excursion Thermo-Rubber surround,4.Parabolic triangular cone geometry support system,5.Removable and reversible screw concealing ring,6.Embedded 12 AWG tinsel leads / dual 8 AWG slot loaded wiring terminal,7.Anodized aluminum voice coil former,8.Mirror image symmetrical spiders,9.Flat edge wound copper clad aluminum voice coil,10.Optimized pole piece and spider venting,11.Optimized for both sealed and vented enclosures,12.Custom insulated/isolated compression terminals,13.Spun-Laced Nomex collar,14.1 Year Standard Warranty', '2016-05-27 16:35:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(633, 133, 'ROCKFORD FOSGATE T1D212 POWER - T1 12 SUBWOOFER', 34990, 10, 'rockford-fosgate-t1d212-power-t1-12-subwoofer.jpg', 'Innovative technologies allow the T1D212 subwoofer to perform like a larger woofer over the previous model. The T1 12” features dual 2-Ohm voice coils, 800 Watts RMS power handling, and includes a grille with integral trim ring. 1.Symmetrical dual progressive roll tear resistant poly-cotton spiders,2.Periodic-stitched fatigue resistant tinsel lead wire,3.Proprietary 8 AWG insulated allmetal input spring terminal connection,4.High-temp voice coil with spun-laced Nomex® re-inforcement collar,5.Optimized and matched magnetic and complicance geometry,6.Anodized aluminum heat sinking dust cap,7.Kevlar fiber reinforced paper cone,8.Rigid die-cast aluminum basket,9.Optimized pole piece and spider venting,10.Anodized aluminum voice coil former / copper clad aluminum wire,11.1 Year Standard Warranty', '2016-05-27 16:35:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(634, 133, 'ROCKFORD FOSGATE P2D412 PUNCH - P2-12 SUBWOOFER', 9990, 10, 'rockford-fosgate-p2d412-punch-p2-12-subwoofer.jpg', 'Rockford Fosgate has always been known as “The PUNCH” and the P2 12" subwoofers certainly continue with the tradition. With their Dual Voice Coils, they are an easy addition to almost any vehicle, the P2 subwoofers perform best in standard sealed and vented enclosures and their double-stacked magnets deliver REAL Bass!', '2016-05-27 16:35:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(635, 133, 'ROCKFORD FOSGATE P1S412 PUNCH - P1-12 SUBWOOFER', 6990, 10, 'rockford-fosgate-p1s412-punch-p1-12-subwoofer.jpg', 'P1S412 12" Punch P1 4-Ohm SVC Subwoofer - The P1 12" subwoofers are a great choice for those looking to add some PUNCH to their system without breaking the bank. They are designed for small enclosures, so they won''t monopolize your trunk space either.1.Custom 10-AWG nickel plated push terminals,2.High density poly-foam surround,3.High-temp voice coil with spun-laced Nomex® re-inforcement collar,4.Linear spider with embedded 16 AWG tinsel leads,5.Parabolic injection molded ABS/Acrylic dustcap,6.Protective PVC textured magnet cover,7.Reversable ABS trim ring,8.Thermoformed polypropylene cone', '2016-05-27 16:35:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(636, 133, 'ROCKFORD FOSGATE R1S412 PRIME - Single Voice Coil-12 SUBWOOFER', 4990, 10, 'rockford-fosgate-r1s412-prime-single-voice-coil-12-subwoofer.jpg', 'Rockford Fosgate Prime 12” subwoofers provide high performance bass at an unbelievable value. The R1S412 features a Single Voice Coil design, 150 Watt RMS power handling, and work great in sealed enclosures. 1.Anodized aluminum voice coil former,2.Parabolic polypropylene cone,3.12 AWG compression terminals,4.Stamped steel basket,5.Single voice coil design,6.Optimized for sealed enclosures,7.1 Year Standard Warranty', '2016-05-27 16:35:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(637, 133, 'ROCKFORD FOSGATE P1S48 PUNCH - P1-8 SUBWOOFER', 5490, 10, 'rockford-fosgate-p1s48-punch-p1-8-subwoofer.jpg', 'Bass for a small space! Optimized for small sealed and vented enclosures, the P1 8" subwoofers are a perfect addition when space is at a premium. Their mounting depth offers a wide variety of install options as well.', '2016-05-27 16:35:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(638, 131, 'Rockford Fosgate Prime R1693', 4500, 10, 'rockford-fosgate-prime-r1693.jpg', 'The R1693 is a 6”x9” 3-way full-range speaker rated at 60 watts RMS for a new generation of factory replacement speakers. Kit includes integrated high-pass crossovers and mounting hardware.1.1/2" (13mm) mylar balanced dome tweeter,2.Foam surround,3.Mica-injected polypropylene cone,4.Stamped steel basket,5.1 Year Standard Warranty', '2016-05-27 16:35:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(639, 131, 'Rockford Fosgate Prime R1653', 3500, 10, 'rockford-fosgate-prime-r1653.jpg', 'Put Rockford Fosgate sound in your car without breaking the bank. Whether you''re building your first system or replacing some burned-out factory speakers, Prime speakers offer clean, powerful performance that''ll keep you and your friends entertained as you drive.The Prime R1653 6-3/4" 3-way speakers sport stiff mica-injected polypropylene woofer cones that deliver strong drums and bass, along with clean reproduction of the midrange frequencies. Mylar tweeters broadcast vibrant highs that add excitement to your music without harshness, while piezo supertweeters bring out the extreme high-frequency details that make your music sound more lively. Built-in crossover networks ensure smooth audio response, so all your music plays faithfully.', '2016-05-27 16:35:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(640, 131, 'Rockford Fosgate Prime R152', 3990, 10, 'rockford-fosgate-prime-r152.jpg', 'The R152 is a 5.25” 2-way full-range speaker rated at 35 watts RMS for a new generation of factory replacement speakers. Kit includes two speakers with grilles, integrated high-pass crossovers and mounting hardware.1.1/2" (13mm) mylar balanced dome tweeter,2.Foam surround,3.Mica-injected polypropylene cone,4.Stamped steel basket,5.1 Year Standard Warranty', '2016-05-27 16:35:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(641, 69, 'Sony XM-GTX60212 Xplod Car Amplifier', 34990, 50, 'sony-xm-gtx60212-xplod-car-amplifier.jpg', '<p><br />\nChannel Configuration 1 (Mono)<br /><br />\nPower Supply Pulse Power Supply<br /><br />\nMaximum Output Power 110W x 2 (at 4 ohms), 350W (BTL, at 4 ohms)<br /><br />\nRated Output Power 60W x 2 (at 4 ohms), 75W x 2 (at 2 ohms), 150W (BTL) (at 4 ohms)<br /><br />\nLow Pass Filter / Slope 80 Hz, 18 dB/oct<br /><br />\nFrequency Response 5-50kHz<br /><br />\nSignal-to-Noise Ratio 93dBA<br /><br />\nTotal Harmonic Distortion (1kHz) 0.05% or less (at 1kHz, 4 ohms)<br /><br />\nInput: Number of Channels 2<br /><br />\nLine In: Input Sensitivity (V) 0.3-6/2.8-12<br /><br />\nDual Mode Capability Yes<br /><br />\nCurrent Drain 15A (at 4 ohms, 60W x 2)<br /><br />\nTolerance +0/-3dB<br /><br />\nDimensions (W x H x D) 326 x 55 x 200mm<br /><br />\nWeight (kg) Approx. 2.0kg<br /></p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(642, 131, 'Hertz DCX 690 -3 Way Dieci 6&x 9&Coaxial Car Speakers 180W', 3990, 50, 'ecx-100-4-co-axial-speaker-2-way-80w.jpg', '<p>An authentic 3-way coax capable of reproducing a wide frequency spectrum. The DCX 690.3 uses an oversized magnetic group, TPU<br />(Thermoplastic polyurethane) surround, a 60 mm diameter midrange and a PEI dome tweeter. The result is linearity, wide dispersion and extra-ordinary efficiency not found in traditional coax components. An involving, emotional sound, even at high SPL levels.<br /><br /><strong>Features</strong>:<br /><br />90W RMS power handling (180W peak)<br />6""x9"" woofer, 60mm mid-range, 15mm tweeter<br />High Density flux ferrite magnet<br />Water repellent pressed paper cone woofer<br />Neodymium magnet<br />Mylar dome tweeter<br />Frequency response: 45-22kHz<br />Impendence: 4-ohms<br />Sensitivity: 95 dB/Spl<br />Outer diameter: 165mm<br />Mounting hole diameter: 152mm<br />Mounting depth: 76mm<br /><br /></p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(643, 132, 'Hertz ET 20 0.75 inch Tweeter (100W)', 2999, 50, 'hertz-et-20-075-inch-tweeter-100w.jpg', '<p style="text-align:justify;"><strong>Features</strong>:</p>\n<ul style="text-align:justify;"><li>The dome high-frequency oscillator ET 20 of woven material Tetolon has an excellent internal damping and light weight.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Combined with the compact and powerful neodymium magnet provides a high sensitivity and the fastest response.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>On the basis of the magnetic system is a special sound-absorbing drive controls the opposite of the dome light and prevents the appearance of unwanted resonances.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>The set includes all necessary installation components allow to realize the best installation solution.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>The diffraction lens is placed in front of the dome, expanding the directional pattern.</li>\n</ul><p style="text-align:justify;"> </p>\n<p style="text-align:justify;"><strong>Specification</strong>:</p>\n<div class="product_detail_main_tbl" style="text-align:justify;">\n<ul><li>Speaker Size [inches]: 0.75<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Number of speaker elements: 1-Way<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Design: Tweeter<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Peak Power Handling [Watts]: 100<br /><br /></li>\n<li>RMS Power Handling [Watts]: 100<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Impedance (per voice coil) [Ohm]: 4<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Shallow Mount Installation: No<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Top Mount Depth [inches]: 0.75<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Tweeter Design: Soft Dome<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Tweeter Composition: Tetolon<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Woofer Composition: Water-Repellent Pressed Paper Cone<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Woofer Surround: Flat Foam Surround<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Sensitivity (Efficiency) [dB]: 91<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Minimum Frequency Response [Hz]: 2000<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Maximum Frequency Response [Hz]: 23000<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Subwoofer Grille (Optional, Included or No): Included</li>\n</ul></div>\n<p>?</p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:10',