(645, 134, 'Sony (XM-GTX6042) In-Car Amplifier', 5990, 50, 'xdi-600-600-w-mono-1-ohm-amp.jpg', '<p>Description:<br />Sony makes one of the best amplifiers in car audio at very reasonable price. Easy Trade Brings you the best prices for Sony''s XM-GTX 6042 with warranty.<br /><br />Feature:<br /><br />Sony presentsCar Amplifier with ultimate features.<br />Sony Xplod XM-GTX6042 GTXSeriesCar Amplifier is of 1 channel.<br />It hasMOSFET Power Supply.<br />5-50kHzFrequency Range.<br />100dB Sensitivity.<br />4 Channels input configuration and +0/-3dBTolerance.<br />It takes 110W 4, 150W 2 + 300W 1maximum power and 70W 4, 60W 4output power.<br />It gives nice layout and look.<br />Amplifiers give more power allowing you to play your music more loudly.<br />It is worth buying cause it is durable and gives great sound quality.<br /><br /><br />Specification:<br /><br />Channel Configuration - 4/3<br /><br /><br />Power Supply - MOSFET Power Supply<br /><br /><br />Maximum Output Power - 150W &amp;times; 2 (at 2 ohms) + 300W &amp;times; 1 (at 4 ohms BTL), 110W &amp;times; 4 (at 4 ohms)<br /><br /><br />Rated Output Power - 70W &amp;times; 4 / 1.0% (at 2 ohms), 60W &amp;times; 4 / 1.0% (at 4 ohms)<br /><br /><br />High Pass Filter / Slope - 80Hz (Variable), -12dB/oct (Selectable)<br /><br /><br />Low Pass Filter / Slope - 80Hz (Variable), 18dB/oct (Selectable)<br /><br /><br />Frequency Response - 5-50kHz<br /><br /><br />Signal-to-Noise Ratio - 100dB<br /><br /><br />Total Harmonic Distortion (1kHz) - 0.05%<br /><br /><br />Input: Number of Channels - 4<br /><br /><br />Tolerance - +0/-3dB<br /><br /><br />Dimensions (W x H x D) - 384 &amp;times; 55 &amp;times; 252mm<br /><br /><br />Weight (kg) - Approx. 3.1kg</p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
