(653, 102, 'ACUSTIKA MINI FUSEHOLDER', 300, 10, 'acustika-mini-fuseholder.jpg', 'This product has got in-line fuse holder for ATM mini fuses. It has heavy duty fuse holder with cover. It also has got number 12 lead wire. Rating is 32 volts and 30 amperes.', '2016-05-27 16:35:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(654, 133, 'POLK AUDIO MM1040-MM SERIES - 10 - Single Voice Coil', 10600, 10, 'polk-audio-mm1040-mm-series-10-single-voice-coil.jpg', 'Need bigger bass? Dude, get a bigger subwoofer. But get the right one, too. The MM1040 high-performance 10" subwoofer to be exact. You can use it in a sealed or ported enclosure. As a result of 3 years of Polk research and development, the new MM subs have been offer unparalleled sound quality with exceptional fit to meet virtually any application, and the MM1040 is no exception.', '2016-05-27 16:35:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(655, 133, 'POLK AUDIO SR104-DVC SR SERIES - 10 DVC - Dual Voice Coil', 16780, 10, 'polk-audio-sr104-dvc-sr-series-10-dvc-dual-voice-coil.jpg', 'SR Subwoofers have massive die-cast aluminum baskets to house the 16 pound motor structure. A 2-1/2" inch glass/epoxy voice coil former wound with four layers of heavy gauge high temperature aluminum wire provides the highest power handling and reliability possible. The voice coil is bathed in cooling air via an extensive network of vents in the pole piece and basket. Specially designed curved vanes smooth the airflow to minimize air turbulence that could cause noise and woofer "chuffing." Dual progressive roll spiders precisely control the cone’s long excursion for the ultimate in tight, detailed and musical bass. NBR (Nitrile Butyl Rubber) Surround damps distortion inducing resonance as it stands up to harsh automotive environments.', '2016-05-27 16:35:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(656, 133, 'POLK AUDIO SR104-SR SERIES - 10 - Single Voice Coil', 16680, 10, 'polk-audio-sr104-sr-series-10-single-voice-coil.jpg', 'SR Subwoofers have massive die-cast aluminum baskets to house the 16 pound motor structure. A 2-1/2" inch glass/epoxy voice coil former wound with four layers of heavy gauge high temperature aluminum wire provides the highest power handling and reliability possible. The voice coil is bathed in cooling air via an extensive network of vents in the pole piece and basket. Specially designed curved vanes smooth the airflow to minimize air turbulence that could cause noise and woofer "chuffing." Du', '2016-05-27 16:35:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(657, 133, 'POLK AUDIO DB1040DVC-db SERIES - 10 DVC - Dual Voice Coil', 9890, 10, 'polk-audio-db1040dvc-db-series-10-dvc-dual-voice-coil.jpg', '10" Dual voil subwoofers optimized for high performance in virtually any enclosure type: sealed, vented and band pass.', '2016-05-27 16:35:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(658, 133, 'POLK AUDIO DB1240DVC-DB SERIES - 12 DVC - Dual Voice Coil', 9600, 10, 'polk-audio-db1240dvc-db-series-12-dvc-dual-voice-coil.jpg', '12" Dual voil subwoofers optimized for high performance in virtually any enclosure type: sealed, vented and band pass. Wrap-around Rubber Gasket seals the sub in your enclosure for airtight performance.', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
