(660, 133, 'POLK AUDIO-DB1212-DB SERIES - Single 12 Enclosure - Subwoofers', 14950, 10, 'polk-audio-db1212-db-series-single-12-enclosure-subwoofers.jpg', 'We''d like to say we won''t bore with the details. But sometimes making a sub better is all about the details. Such is the case with our Single and Dual 12-inch sub enclosures. We took what we knew worked from our db212, did a little refining to make this next generation more impressive, then added even more blow-you-away performance. The result is just plain nasty. Which is good.', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(661, 133, 'POLK AUDIO DXi124-DXi SERIES - 12 - Subwoofers', 9200, 10, 'polk-audio-dxi124-dxi-series-12-subwoofers.jpg', '1 - 12" Diameter (30.48cm) Dynamic Balance polymer composite cone', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(662, 133, 'POLK AUDIO DXi112-DXi SERIES - 12 Boxes - Subwoofers', 10900, 10, 'polk-audio-dxi112-dxi-series-12-boxes-subwoofers.jpg', '1 - 12" Diameter (30.48cm) Dynamic Balance polymer composite cone', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(663, 133, 'POLK AUDIO MM1240-DVC-MM SERIES - 12 DVC - Dual Voice Coil', 13500, 10, 'polk-audio-mm1240-dvc-mm-series-12-dvc-dual-voice-coil.jpg', 'So you want to be able to do more with your big, nasty subwoofer. Welcome to nastyville, otherwise known as the MM1240DVC high performance 12" subwoofer. With 425 watt continuous/800 watt peak, this subwoofer is for serious bassheads. Everything you''ve ever wanted in a subwoofer, including easy installation.', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(664, 133, 'POLK AUDIO SR124-SR SERIES - 12 - Single Voice Coil', 16485, 10, 'polk-audio-sr124-sr-series-12-single-voice-coil.jpg', 'SR Subwoofers have massive die-cast aluminum baskets to house the 16 pound motor structure. A 2-1/2" inch glass/epoxy voice coil former wound with four layers of heavy gauge high temperature aluminum wire provides the highest power handling and reliability possible. The voice coil is bathed in cooling air via an extensive network of vents in the pole piece and basket. Specially designed curved vanes smooth the airflow to minimize air turbulence that could cause noise and woofer "chuffing." Dual progressive roll spiders precisely control the cone’s long excursion for the ultimate in tight, detailed and musical bass. NBR (Nitrile Butyl Rubber) Surround damps distortion inducing resonance as it stands up to harsh automotive environments.', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(665, 133, 'POLK AUDIO MM840-MM SERIES - 8 - Single Voice Coil', 6750, 10, 'polk-audio-mm840-mm-series-8-single-voice-coil.jpg', 'If you''re looking for big bass that doesn''t take up much space, the MM840 8-inch subwoofer is the right choice. Using carbon composite baskets, powerful motor structures with oversized voice coils, the MM840 punches out real tight, real serious bass you''d usually find only in the most expensive loudspeaker systems. With 250 watt continuous/500 watt peak power handling, we recommend the MM840 for small sealed (.35 cubic foot) enclosures.', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(666, 133, 'POLK AUDIO-MM840-DVC-MM SERIES - 8 DVC - Dual Voice Coil', 6750, 10, 'polk-audio-mm840-dvc-mm-series-8-dvc-dual-voice-coil.jpg', 'When you want more wiring options to get the most performance from your subwoofer, check out our Dual Voice Coil MM840 8-inch subwoofer. It''s the same easy-to-install compact size as the Single Voice Coil. And it has all the MM signature features: carbon composite baskets, powerful motor structures with oversized voice coils. The MM840 punches out real tight, real serious bass, the kind usually found only in the most expensive systems. With 250 watt continuous/500 watt peak power handling, we recommend the MM840 for small sealed (.35 cubic foot) enclosures.', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(667, 133, 'POLK AUDIO DB840-DB SERIES - 8 - Single Voice Coil', 4500, 10, 'polk-audio-db840-db-series-8-single-voice-coil.jpg', '8" Single voil subwoofers optimized for high performance in virtually any enclosure type: sealed, vented and band pass.', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(668, 131, 'Polk Audio db6501', 8750, 10, 'polk-audio-db6501.jpg', 'Polk Audio db6501 component speaker system features 6-1/2? woofers made from a polymer/mica composite and durable rubber surrounds that won’t fall apart under stress from heat, moisture, or time. Liquid-cooled 1? silk/polymer dome tweeters use powerful Neodymium magnets to deliver precise high-frequency reproduction, enveloping you in bright musical detail. You can surface- or flush-mount the tweeters with the included swivel-mount cups. Just aim the tweeters so they broadcast toward your ears, creating a powerful stereo image.', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(669, 131, 'Polk Audio db5251', 8250, 10, 'polk-audio-db5251.jpg', 'Polk Audio’s db5251 component speaker system features 5-1/4? woofers made from a polymer/mica composite and durable rubber surrounds that won’t fall apart under stress from heat, moisture, or time. Liquid-cooled 1? silk/polymer dome tweeters use powerful Neodymium magnets to deliver precise high-frequency reproduction, enveloping you in bright musical detail. You can surface- or flush-mount the tweeters with the included swivel-mount cups. Just aim the tweeters so they broadcast toward your ears, creating a powerful stereo image.', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(670, 131, 'Polk Audio db691', 7500, 10, 'polk-audio-db691.jpg', 'Polk Audio db691, 6?x9? speakers, are legendary in their crisp-clear music and tight bass. With db691?s you can’t miss a descent bass note, that every composer uses to create the background effects.db691 is an upgrade over Polk Audio db690 with more frequency response range.Again, like all its siblings in db Series speakers, db691 features High Efficiency Design, meaning less amplifier power needed for more audio output. Meaning better sound and more volume using less power. The bottom line is db Loudspeakers will definitely blow you and your friends away, whether they’re driven by aftermarket head units or factory installed electronics.Polk Audio db691 can be fitted in most cars in factory locations with small alterations in the rear tray, or by using a quality MDF plank.', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(671, 131, 'Polk Audio db651', 4350, 10, 'polk-audio-db651.jpg', 'Polk Audio’s db Series speakers feature High Efficiency Design, meaning less amplifier power needed for more audio output. Meaning better sound and more volume using less power. The bottom line is db Loudspeakers will definitely blow you and your friends away, whether they’re driven by aftermarket head units or factory installed electronics.All db Series drivers, tweeters and Subwoofers use Polk audio’s Dynamic Balance technology, which they developed in conjunction with the Johns Hopkins University. The result is an undistorted music by eliminating cone resonance.Polk Audio db651 – 6-1/2? Coaxial speakers are best fit in most car door positions.', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(672, 131, 'Polk Audio db521', 4090, 10, 'polk-audio-db521.jpg', 'Polk Audio’s db Series speakers feature High Efficiency Design, meaning less amplifier power needed for more audio output. Meaning better sound and more volume using less power. The bottom line is db Loudspeakers will definitely blow you and your friends away, whether they’re driven by aftermarket head units or factory installed electronics.All db Series drivers, tweeters and Subwoofers use Polk audio’s Dynamic Balance technology, which they developed in conjunction with the Johns Hopkins University. The result is an undistorted music by eliminating cone resonance.Polk Audio db521?s having 93dB sensitivity, can be easily powered directly from the head unit.', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(673, 133, 'DB 571 5 X 7 Coaxial  CPH 60 W(RMS)  PPH 180W', 6000, 10, 'db-571-5-x-7-coaxial-cph-60-wrms-pph-180w.jpg', 'For a quick and easy install, with very little sonic compromise, choose the db571. It''s an ultra-high-performance 5"x7" mid-woofer and 1-inch silk dome tweeter have a frequency response of 52Hz-22kHz and a sensitivity of 93db. The db571 is suitable for either a vehicle or boat. Like all db Series speakers, the db571 will fit virtually any factory application.', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(674, 131, 'Sony (XS-GTF16272) 16cm 2-Way In-Car Speaker', 1990, 50, 'sony-xs-gtf16272-16cm-2-way-in-car-speaker.jpg', '<p>Description:<br />Sony India Brings To You Sony Car Audio Devices To Make Your Car A True Entertainment Hub! Sony Is The Largest Brand In The World When It Comes To Electronics, Especially Audio Products. Sony Corporation Is Synonymous With Highest Quality And Commitment To Customer Service. Sony Car Audio Products Are Trusted For Their Quality And Excellent Features. Sony India, One Of The Trusted Sony Car Audio Traders, Offers A Comprehensive Range Of Car Audio Products Including Sony Amplifiers, Sony Subwoofers, Sony Speakers And More.<br /><br />Feature:<br /><br />Full Range 2-Way Coaxial Speaker.<br />190W Peak Power.<br />40W Rated Power.<br />HOP + ACFM (Aramid and Carbon Fiber Matrix) woofer for rich bass and clear vocal.<br />PEN (Polyethylene Naphthalate) tweeter for smooth and clear high sound.<br /><br /><br />Specification:<br /><br />General:<br /><br />Diameter - 16cm<br />Speaker System - 2-Way Coaxial<br />Peak Power (W) - 190<br />Rated Input Power (W) - 40<br />Sensitivity - 91 &amp;plusmn; 2dB/W/m<br /><br /><br />Woofer:<br /><br />Type - Cone<br />Edge - Cloth<br /><br /><br />Mid-Range:<br /><br />Type - B.D. (Balanced Dome)<br />Size - &amp;Phi;35mm<br /><br /></p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(675, 133, 'MM 571 5 x 7 Coaxial  CPH 90W (RMS)  PPH 200W', 13500, 10, 'mm-571-5-x-7-coaxial-cph-90w-rms-pph-200w.jpg', 'For a quick and easy install, with very little sonic compromise, choose the MM571. It''s an ultra-high-performance 5"x7" mid-woofer and 1-inch silk dome tweeter have a frequency response of 38Hz-25kHz and a sensitivity of 92db. The MM571 is suitable for either a vehicle or boat. Like all MM Series speakers, the MM571 will fit virtually any application.', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(676, 133, 'MM 691 6 x 9 3-way  CPH 125W (RMS)  PPH 300W', 16500, 10, 'mm-691-6-x-9-3-way-cph-125w-rms-pph-300w.jpg', 'Want more performance but don''t want to go the component route? Choose the MM691 3-way. You get a woofer and tweeter, plus a dedicated midrange driver for the absolutely crucial mid-frequencies. That extra mid-range energy can create more uniform sound overall. The MM691 has the all MM goodies, which makes it a real standout in virtually any install.', '2016-05-27 16:35:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(677, 133, 'DB 351 3 1/2 Coaxial  CPH 35W (RMS)  PPH 105W', 4000, 10, 'db-351-3-1-2-coaxial-cph-35w-rms-pph-105w.jpg', 'The db351 is a great in-dash or rear seat speaker. It''s compactness makes it an easy fit, but it''s big on all the Polk technology that makes it uniquely db: meaning you get legendary Polk sound at a terrific price.', '2016-05-27 16:35:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
