(678, 133, 'DB 651 S 6 1/2 Slim Mnt Coaxial  CPH 55 W(RMS)  PPH 165W', 5100, 10, 'db-651-s-6-1-2-slim-mnt-coaxial-cph-55-wrms-pph-165w.jpg', 'Turn up your vehicle''s audio performance with the db651, a 6-1/2-inch coax speaker designed to drop into a variety of applications in no time at all. Advanced materials reduce component weight while offering rock solid reliability, advanced looks and ultra high performance. Borrowing technology from our flagship SR Series, the db Series offers exceptional value for the price.', '2016-05-27 16:35:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(679, 131, 'Sony (XS-GT69312) 3-Way In-Car Speakers', 3990, 50, 'mm-521-5-1-4-coaxial-cph-90w-rms-pph-200w.jpg', '<p>Description:<br />Sony India Brings To You Sony Car Audio Devices To Make Your Car A True Entertainment Hub! Sony Is The Largest Brand In The World When It Comes To Electronics, Especially Audio Products. Sony Corporation Is Synonymous With Highest Quality And Commitment To Customer Service. Sony Car Audio Products Are Trusted For Their Quality And Excellent Features. Sony India, One Of The Trusted Sony Car Audio Traders, Offers A Comprehensive Range Of Car Audio Products Including Sony Amplifiers, Sony Subwoofers, Sony Speakers And More.<br /><br />Feature:<br /><br />16cm x 24cm 3-Way In-Car Speaker.<br />16cm x 24cm GTX Series Full Range 3-Way Coaxial Speaker.<br />Full Range 3-Way Coaxial Speaker.<br />400W Peak Power,3.100W Rated Power.<br />Rubber coated cloth surround Edge.<br />H.O.P. + aramid fiber cone woofer for rich and deep bass.<br />Stroke Stabilizer Surround.<br /><br /><br />Specification:<br /><br />General:<br /><br />Diameter - 16cm x 24cm<br />Speaker System - 3-Way Coaxial<br />Peak Power (W) - 400<br />Rated Input Power (W) - 100<br />Sensitivity - 91&amp;plusmn;2dB/W/m<br /><br /><br />Woofer:<br /><br />Type - HOP + Aramid Fiber Cone<br />Magnet - Ferrite<br />Edge - Rubber coated cloth surround<br /><br /><br />Mid-Range:<br /><br />Type - Cone<br />Size - &amp;Phi;66mm<br />Magnet / Size - Ferrite / &amp;Phi;50mm<br /><br /><br />Tweeter:<br /><br />Type - B.D (Piezo)<br />Size - &amp;Phi;25mm<br /><br /></p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(680, 131, 'JVC drvn Series 16cm 2-Way Coaxial Speakers (CS-V627)', 2190, 50, 'mm-651-6-1-2-coaxial-cph-100w-rms-pph-200w.jpg', '<p>Features<br /><br />2-Way Coaxial<br /><br /><br />230W Peak/40W RMS Power<br /><br /><br />Frequency Response: 45 - 25,000Hz<br /><br /><br />Sound Pressure Level: 89dB/W.m<br /><br /><br />Crossover Frequency: 5kHz<br /><br /><br />Carbon Mica Cone Woofer<br /><br /><br />Poly-Ether Imide Balanced Tweeter<br /><br /><br />Strontium Ferrite Magnet (Woofer)<br /><br /><br />Neodymium Magnet (Tweeter)<br /><br /><br />Hybrid Surround<br /><br /><br />Mounting Depth: 43.5 mm</p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(681, 131, 'JVC drvn V Series 16cm 2-Way Component Speakers (CS-VS607)', 5990, 50, 'mm-5251-5-1-4-component-cph-90w-rms-pph-200w.jpg', '<p>Features<br /><br />2-Way Component<br /><br /><br />300W Peak/60W RMS Power<br /><br /><br />Frequency Response: 45 - 28,000Hz<br /><br /><br />Sound Pressure Level: 87dB/W.m<br /><br /><br />Carbon Mica Cone Woofer<br /><br /><br />Poly-Ether Imide Balanced Tweeter<br /><br /><br />Strontium Ferrite Magnet (Woofer)<br /><br /><br />Neodymium Magnet (Tweeter)<br /><br /><br />In-Line Network<br /><br /><br />Hybrid Surround<br /><br /><br />Mounting Depth: 56.5 mm</p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(683, 132, 'DB 1001 1 Tweeter  CPH 60W(RMS)  PPH 180W', 3500, 10, 'db-1001-1-tweeter-cph-60wrms-pph-180w.jpg', 'The db1001 works well in OEM factory systems, as well as with high-powered aftermarket head units and component power amps. The db1001 delivers classic Polk Audio performance and durability like never before.You won''t find a sweeter tweeter.', '2016-05-27 16:35:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(684, 133, 'DB 10G 10 Sub Woofer Grill', 2000, 10, 'db-10g-10-sub-woofer-grill.jpg', 'Polk Audio''s db10G 10" subwoofer grille uses sturdy ABS plastic construction to protect your db1040 or db1040DVC component sub against harm. The rugged grille also adds a stylish look to your installation, complementing the great bass coming out of your vehicle. Warranty: 30 days.', '2016-05-27 16:35:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(685, 133, 'MM 10G 10 Woofer Grill', 2000, 10, 'mm-10g-10-woofer-grill.jpg', 'Protect your Polk Audio Mobile Monitor series subwoofer with this sturdy ABS plastic grille. The black and silver-spoked style complements the "wagon wheel" design of your 10" MM1040 or MM1040D subwoofer basket, so your sub looks good from any angle.', '2016-05-27 16:35:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(686, 133, 'DB 12G 12 Sub Woofer Grill', 2200, 10, 'db-12g-12-sub-woofer-grill.jpg', 'Diameter: 12 Inch', '2016-05-27 16:35:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(687, 133, 'DB 1222 12 Dual Woofer  CPH 720W(RMS)  PPH 1500W', 28000, 10, 'db-1222-12-dual-woofer-cph-720wrms-pph-1500w.jpg', 'We''d like to say we won''t bore with the details. But sometimes making a sub better is all about the details. Such is the case with our Single and Dual 12-inch sub enclosures. We took what we knew worked from our db212, did a little refining to make this next generation more impressive, then added even more blow-you-away performance. The result is just plain nasty. Which is good.', '2016-05-27 16:35:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(688, 133, 'MM 1540 15 Woofer  CPH 425W (RMS)  PPH 850W  4 OHM', 21000, 10, 'mm-1540-15-woofer-cph-425w-rms-pph-850w-4-ohm.jpg', 'Introducing the new Mobile Monitor (MM) Series high performance loudspeaker systems, the next generation in mobile loudspeaker design. The MM Series features 18 new models, including 3 Ultra Marine designs, to fit virtually any application on land and water. The MM Series is composed of 6 full range systems, 3 component packages and 9 subwoofers. As a result of 3 years of Polk research and development, the new MM systems have been designed to offer unparalleled sound quality with exceptional fit to meet virtually any application. Borrowing technology from our flagship SR Series, the MM Series offers exceptional value for the price. Through the use of high-tech carbon composite baskets, powerful Neodymium motor structures using oversized voice coils, and state-of-the-art woven glass composite cones, we offer high-end audio performance normally found only in the most expensive loudspeaker systems. In addition, these space age materials offer weight savings that can mean higher performance for your car or boat.', '2016-05-27 16:35:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(689, 133, 'MM 12G 12 Woofer Grill', 2200, 10, 'mm-12g-12-woofer-grill.jpg', 'Protect your Polk Audio Mobile Monitor series subwoofer with this sturdy ABS plastic grille. The black and silver-spoked style complements the "wagon wheel" design of your 12" MM1240 or MM1240D subwoofer basket, so your sub looks good from any angle. Warranty: 1 year.', '2016-05-27 16:35:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(690, 133, 'MM 15G 15 Woofer Grill', 2300, 10, 'mm-15g-15-woofer-grill.jpg', '15G Protect your Polk Audio Monitor Series Mobile 15 `subwoofer with this sturdy ABS plastic grille. The black and silver spokes-style complements the `Wagon Wheel` of your design or MM1540D MM1540 Subwoofer place, so your sub looks good from every angle.', '2016-05-27 16:35:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(691, 133, 'DB 8G 8 Sub Woofer Grill', 1800, 10, 'db-8g-8-sub-woofer-grill.jpg', 'Polk Audio''s db8G 8" subwoofer grille uses sturdy ABS plastic construction to protect your db840 or db840DVC component sub against harm. The rugged grille also adds a stylish look to your installation, complementing the great bass coming out of your vehicle. Warranty: 30 days.', '2016-05-27 16:35:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
