(715, 135, 'JVC Double Din Screen Car Stereo CD/DVD Multimedia AV USB iPod Player', 19990, 50, 'jvc-double-din-screen-car-stereo-cd-dvd-multimedia-av-usb-ipod-player.jpg', '<p><strong>Description</strong>:<br />The JVC KW-AV50 DVD receiver won''t just transform the look of your dash &amp;mdash; it''ll give your daily commute, road trips, and grocery runs a makeover, too. It gives you a touchscreen entertainment command center that''ll handle all your tunes, become best friends with your iPod&amp;reg; and iPhone&amp;reg;, and even play movies while you''re parked. And unlike many other DVD receivers, you can remove its control panel for added security.<br /><br /><strong>Feature</strong>:<br /><br /><br />DVD/CD player with AM/FM tuner<br />built-in amplifier (20 watts RMS CEA-2006/50 peak x 4 channels)<br />6.1"" touchscreen with detachable face<br />colors can be adjusted separately for background, text, and buttons (31 choices)<br />fits double-DIN (4"" tall) dash openings<br /><br /><br />Audio/Visual Features:<br /><br /><br />plays CDs, DVDs, and USB memory devices (see ""Details"" for full capabilities)<br />3-band parametric EQ, high-pass/low-pass filters<br /><br /><strong>Expandability</strong>:<br /><br />iPod control: JVC KS-U30 cable required for full access to audio/video content<br />works with JVC satellite radio tuner, Bluetooth adapter, HD Radio&amp;trade; tuner (not included)<br />inputs: rear USB input, front panel aux in, rear A/V inputs, rear-view camera input<br />outputs: video output; 5-channel preamp outputs (4-volt front, rear, mono subwoofer)<br /><br /></p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
