(717, 131, 'Kenwood 6-1/2 inch 2-Way Car Speakers', 1990, 50, 'kenwood-kfc-e1662180w.jpg', '<p><strong>Description:</strong></p>\n<p><br />Kenwood''s KFC-G1620 6-1/2"" speakers revitalize your car''s audio system with strong bass and plenty of musical detail. These speakers bring out the best in your favorite tunes, with a lively sound that''ll make a long drive seem a lot shorter.<br />These Kenwoods feature lightweight, rigid polypropylene cones that offer good bass response and rich midrange, while the balanced dome tweeters broadcast radiant highs that add sparkle and dimension to your listening experience. Reliable treated cloth surrounds stand up to the demanding car environment, so you can count on these speakers to keep dishing out superior sound in the long run. These speakers also fit in the 6-3/4"" openings found in many vehicles.<br /><br /><strong>Feature</strong>:<br /><br />2-way car speakers for 6-3/4"" and 6-1/2"" locations (pair)<br />polypropylene woofer<br />treated cloth surround<br />1"" PET (polyethylene terephthalate) balanced dome tweeter<br />power range: 2-30 watts RMS (180 watts peak)<br />frequency response: 45-25,000 Hz<br /><br /><strong>Specification</strong>:<br /><br />Sensitivity: 86 dB at 1W<br />Frequency Response: 45 - 35kHz<br />RMS Power Handling: 2-30W<br />Peak Power Handling: 180W<br />Impedance: 4 ohms<br />Top-Mount Depth: 2.25""<br />Bottom-Mount Depth: 2.43""<br />Cutout Diameter: 5""<br /><br /></p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(718, 131, 'Kenwood Peak Power 3-way Flush Mount Car Speaker 260w', 2490, 50, 'kenwood-kfc-m1632a260w.jpg', '<p><strong>Description:</strong><br /><br />Kenwood KFC M1632A (260W), a 3-way 3-speaker system is what you need for your car music system. The Kenwood KFC M1632A (260W) comes with a pair of Grille and Speaker cable, injection cone woofer, new angled direct sound, 40mm water resistance cone and 9mm ceramic. The Kenwood speaker handles an impressive 180 Watts of power and gives loud and clear sound.<br /><br /><strong>Feature</strong>:<br /><br />3-way 3-speaker System.<br />New Angled Direct Sound.<br />40mm Water Resistance Cone .<br />Supplied with a pair of Grille and Speaker Cable (4.5m).<br />160mm injection P.P Cone Woofer.<br />9mm P.E.I. Dome.<br /><br /><strong>Specification</strong>:<br /><br />Sensitivity: 91dB at 1m<br />Frequency Response: 35-25k Hz<br />Impedance: 4 ohms<br />Size (WHD): 158.0mm x 158.0mm x 66.3mm<br />Mounting Depth: 43.0mm<br />Net Weight: 633g (with Grille)<br />Magnet Weight: 150g</p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
