(725, 100, 'Combo of (ABRO Carnauba Wax & Premium Gold Car Wash)', 741, 10, 'combo-of-abro-carnauba-wax-premium-gold-car-wash.jpg', '<p><strong>A. ?CARNAUBA LIQUID WAX:</strong><br />Quick Overview<br /><br />Premium Liquid Wax from ABRO, USA Shines, Protects and renews paint color Ensures long lasting high gloss shine Restores and Protects painted surfaces With UV Protection Quantity – 473ml Recommended for your car – Protects against UV rays and restores shine and paint color.<br /><br />Description:<br /><br />For the recommended word in car exterior care, check out this Premium Liquid Wax from ABRO, USA<br />If you would love to have long-lasting high gloss shine for your car and protect its painted surfaces from UV rays, this product is for you!<br /><br />Key Benefits:<br /><br />&gt; Easy to apply and wipe off<br />&gt; Ensures long lasting high gloss shine<br />&gt; Restores and protects painted surfaces???<br /> <br /><strong>B. PREMIUM GOLD CAR WASH</strong></p>\r\n<p>FEATURES &amp; BENEFITS<br /><br />- Cuts through stubborn dirt and road film.<br />- Concentrated power to give more quantity of deep cleaning foam.<br />- Every wash cleans, shines and protects.<br />- Full strength, remove bugs &amp; tar.<br /><br />HOW TO USE<br />Mix one (1) ounce of Premium ABRO Gold to each gallon of water. Thoroughly rinse car with water to wash away loose dirt or heavy soil. Apply with sponge or soft cotton cloth, starting at the top and working down to all areas of the car for a thorough washing and even distribution of wax. Rinse each section as you wash to prevent soap solution from drying on surface. Dry with ABRO chamois or 100% cotton cloth.???<br /> <br /><strong>C. FOAMING TIRE CLEANER</strong></p>\r\n<p>Features and Benefites:</p>\r\n<p>- Instantly dissolves road grime with no wiping or rinsing.<br />- Effective on dry or wet tire sidewalls<br />- Leaves a rich, satin finish.</p>\r\n<p><br />HOW TO USE</p>\r\n<p>?Shake can well before use. ABRO FOAMING TIRE CLEANER may be applied to wet or dry tires. To ensure even coverage, hold can 6” from sidewall and spray in a circular, sweeping motion. Allow foam to dissolve and penetrate. No wiping is necessary. Dries in minutes. Do not spray on brake rotors or drums, floor mats, motorcycle tires or seats. Avoid contact with custom rims and painted metal surfaces. Wipe off any overspray.???</p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
