(752, 118, 'ABRO Fire Extinguisher w/Clip Aerosol - 400 ml', 621, 74, 'abro-fire-extinguisher-w-clip-aerosol-400-ml.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>ABRO FE-935 Portable Fire Extinguisher</strong> is non-toxic and ideal for home, auto, and marine use. </span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">The ABRO FE-935 contains an environmentally friendly formula and comes with a convenient fluorescent mounting clip to easily locate your extinguisher in case of fire.?</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Key Features:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong><br /></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">• Ideal for Home, Auto and Marine Use, Non-Toxic, Environmentally Friendly Formula</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">• Convenient Fluorescent Mounting Clip Included?</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">  Use the ABRO FE-935 on minor fires in their initial stages.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">  Contact your local fire department immediately if not completely extinguished?</span></p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
