(764, 137, 'PrimoGPS - PG711G - Car Navigator GPS System', 14499, 38, 'primogps-pg711g-car-navigator-gps-system.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong><span style="color:#374853;line-height:1.6em;">Description of PrimoGPS - PG711G - Car Navigator GPS System</span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong><span style="color:#374853;line-height:1.6em;"> </span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">This is<strong> THE </strong>top choice for anyone who buys gadgets by the inch. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">You won''t find this much screen real estate for this little cash with any other GPS on the market!</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"> With a screen size of <strong>7"</strong>, its crystal clear touch screen, with a resolution of 800 x 480 pixels, gives you a perfect view.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">It is pre-loaded with the latest All India Maps with turn-by-turn directions (in 10 Indian languages) from <strong>MapMyIndia</strong>. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">The maps cover <strong>4787 cities</strong> and more than <strong>1 crore Points of Interest (POI)</strong> so wherever you go, chances are, we''ve got your destination covered!</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">It not just navigates but also provides a whole host of other features - <strong>Bluetooth</strong> for Handsfree Calling, <strong>AVIN Port</strong> for Reverse Camera, and <strong>Multimedia Features</strong> such as Music Player, Video Player, Picture Viewer, E-book reader, FM Transmitter, and much more!</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">The device has <strong>4GB of Internal Memory</strong>, which can be used to load your Music and Video files to play them while on the move! </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">It also has in-built GPS Receiver and in-built Speakers along with Headphone Jack. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">The in-built Battery, it can be recharged with either the car charger or via USB.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">You can now literally go off the beaten track and explore the country like never before. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">With Primo GPS, new roads and new destinations will become a part of your life. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">A perfect travel companion as you navigate your way! Extremely light weight, it''s the perfect guide for the roads. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>The model combines the best of navigation and entertainment right at your finger tips!</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>Specifications -</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td colspan="2">\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>Hardware</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><td>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">Screen Size</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">7" (17.8cms) diagonal touchscreen</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><td>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">Screen Resolution</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">800 x 480 pixels</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><td>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">Internal Memory</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">4GB</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><td>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">RAM</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">128MB</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><td>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">In-built Bluetooth</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">Yes</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><td>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">In-built AVIN Port</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">Yes</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr><td>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">In-built GPS r