(777, 158, 'DecalStyle Side Sticker 2201', 1235, 35, 'decalstyle-side-sticker-2201.jpg', '<p><span><strong>Note:</strong> Size: 13"h x 60"w - You will receive a set of 2 decals (for both sides of the car)</span>??</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;">Personalize your car with our unique decals - stickers. For your guidance, each order will be provided with detailed application instructions.</span><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><span style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;">Key Features -</span><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><span style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;">- All side decals are available as a set of 2 (for both sides of your car).</span><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><span style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;">- These decals / stickers are made from the finest quality self adhesive vinyl which is fade resistant, waterproof and won''t chip or crack.</span><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><span style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;">- You can apply them to the sides, hood, rear or windshield of your car.</span><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><span style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;">- These decals are DIY (Do It Yourself) and you can easily apply them on your own.</span><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><span style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;">- Detailed application instructions shall be provided with the order.</span><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><span style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;">- When you want to remove the graphic from your car, just peel it off</span><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><span style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;">Application Instructions</span><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><span style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;">Step1: Decals/designs come in 3 layers. Top layer is the clear film, Middle layer is the actual decal and Bottom layer is the backing paper</span><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: no