(809, 158, 'DecalStyle Floral Spiral Girly Side Sticker 22103', 1235, 34, 'decalstyle-floral-spiral-girly-side-sticker-22103.jpg', '<p>Personalize your car with our unique decals - stickers. For your guidance, each order will be provided with detailed application instructions. Key Features - - All side decals are available as a set of 2 (for both sides of your car). - These decals / stickers are made from the finest quality self adhesive vinyl which is fade resistant, waterproof and won''t chip or crack. - You can apply them to the sides, hood, rear or windshield of your car. - These decals are DIY (Do It Yourself) and you can easily apply them on your own. - Detailed application instructions shall be provided with the order. - When you want to remove the graphic from your car, just peel it off Application Instructions Step1: Decals/designs come in 3 layers. Top layer is the clear film, Middle layer is the actual decal and Bottom layer is the backing paper Step 2: Take the plastic squeegee (provided free with every order)/ an old credit card will do too Step 3: On a flat surface, rub design to bond it to clear film Step 4: Remove the backing paper. So you have the clear film with the decal stuck on it Step 5: Place your design on the surface you wish to apply to. Rub the design with the squeegee from the center outwards. This will remove all air bubbles. Step 6: Slowly peel off the clear film. Peel it off parallel to the surface. This is it! You are done with applying the decal.</p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
