(818, 158, 'DecalStyle Car Hood Sticker 2224', 781, 35, 'decalstyle-car-hood-sticker-2224.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Note: Size: 20"h x 16"w</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Personalize your car with our unique decals - stickers. </span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">For your guidance, each order will be provided with detailed application instructions.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Key Features</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- All  side decals are available for hood/bonnet of your car.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- These decals / stickers are made from the finest quality self adhesive vinyl which is fade resistant, waterproof and won''t chip or crack.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- You can apply them to the sides, hood, rear or windshield of your car.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- These decals are DIY (Do It Yourself) and you can easily apply them on your own.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- Detailed application instructions shall be provided with the order.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- When you want to remove the graphic from your car, just peel it off</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Application Instructions:</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Step 1: Decals/designs come in 3 layers. Top layer is the clear film, Middle layer is the actual decal and Bottom layer is the backing paper</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Step 2: Take the plastic squeegee (provided free with every order)/ an  old credit card will do too</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Step 3: On a flat surface, rub design to bond it to clear film</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Step 4: Remove the backing paper. So you have the clear film with the decal