(888, 171, 'Paint Protection Solution - by Carnation', 3995, 1000, 'paint-protection-solution-by-carnation.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Application of protective chemical coating to safeguard the exterior paint surface of car against natural elements.</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Car Paint protection is the performance of an extremely thorough cleaning, polishing and waxing of an automobile, to produce a show-quality level of detail. Besides improving the appearance of cars, detailing helps to preserve the car, and thus, increases its resale value.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Paint protection retains the new look of the car by providing a polymeric protective film coating, above the vehicle’s paint work, on the clear coat, which protects against regular automatic car wash scratches, fading of paint, bird droppings, UV rays, acid rain, retaining the gloss and shine.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Once you get paint protection, you won’t need to polish the car for at least one year.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Paint protection enhances shine and seals the natural paint finish by filling in the castellation in every painted and clear coat surface where dirt, grime and pollutants can collect. Once the protection is complete, no chemical residue or coating remains on the paint.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><a href="http://shop.cardekho.com/carnation-faq.html" target="_blank">How to Avail Service</a>? </span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><a href="http://shop.cardekho.com/carnation-hubs.html" target="_blank">Where to Avail this Service</a>?</span></div>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">??</span></p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(891, 268, 'Anti Rust Coating - by Carnation', 3540, 400, 'anti-rust-coating-by-carnation.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Application of protective chemical coating on the underbody of the car to safeguard it against rusting.</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Cars are subjected to abrasion, which peels paint off, and eventually exposes metal to the corrosive effects of the environment. Under coating protects from corrosion, resists abrasion, deadens the sound, and covers weld and minor repairs.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> It’s always better to get an anti-corrosion coating done if you stay in a coastal area or city where pollution may lead to abrasion or paint peeling problem. </span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Anti rust coating forms protective coatin and protect the car against corrosion which happens due to moisture and chemical ingress.</span><br />?</p>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><a href="http://shop.cardekho.com/carnation-faq.html" target="_blank">How to Avail Service</a>? </span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><a href="http://shop.cardekho.com/carnation-hubs.html" target="_blank">Where to Avail this Service</a>?</span></div>\r\n<p>?</p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(894, 268, 'Complete  Car Protection Package -  by Carnation', 7885, 400, 'complete-car-protection-package-by-carnation.jpg', '<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>The combiation pack of overall protection of your car against natural elements.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Car Wash</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Cleaning of the exterior and underbody of the vehicle with pressurized water and with application of Shampoo.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Wash your car regularly! Things like bugs, bird''s dropping, or limestone dripping damage the paint leaving permanent stains if not washed off in time.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">In winter time, the chrome wheels and other chrome trim parts could be damaged by corrosion if the vehicle is not washed after driving on the roads when the salt was used. </span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal;"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">When the car is clean, all the moisture dries up quickly, but when it''s dirty, the moisture accumulates in dirty areas causing corrosion.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">The pressure wash removes the dirt from difficult to reach areas that speed up the corrosion process. Pressure wash also cleans all the dirt from the windshield. The sand that left out on the windshield gets caught by the windshield wipers blades and scratches the windshield when the wipers are operating. </span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal;"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Clean the leaves and other debris from the areas below the windshield and the water channels under the hood and trunk is important, as the leaves block the water drains and collect the moisture, speeding up the corrosion process and causing a damp smell inside your car.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Paint Protection</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Application of protective chemical coating to safeguard the exterior paint surface of car against natural elements.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Car Paint protection is the performance of an extremely thorough cleaning, polishing and waxing of an automobile, to produce a show-quality level of detail. Besides improving the appearance of cars, detailing helps to preserve the car, and thus, increases its resale value.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Paint protection retains the new look of the car by providing a polymeric protective film coating, above the vehicle’s paint work, on the clear coat, which protects against regular automatic car wash scratches, fading of paint, bird droppings, UV rays, acid rain, retaining the gloss and shine.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Once you get paint protection, you won’t need to polish the car for at least one year.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Paint protection enhances shine and seals the natural paint finish by filling in the castellation in every painted and clear coat surface where dirt, grime and pollutants can collect. Once the protection is complete, no chemical residue or coating remains on the paint.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Anti Rust Coating</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Application of protective chemical coating on the underbody of the car to safeguard it against rusting.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Cars are subjected to abrasion, which peels paint off, and eventually exposes metal to the corrosive effects of the environment. Under coating protects from corrosion, resists abrasion, deadens the sound, and covers weld and minor repairs.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">It’s always better to get an anti-corrosion coating done if you stay in a coastal area or city where pollution may lead to abrasion or paint peeling problem. </span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Anti rust coating forms protective coatin and protect the car against corrosion which happens due to moisture and chemical ingress.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"> </p>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><a href="http://shop.cardekho.com/carnation-faq.html" target="_blank">How to Avail Service</a>? </span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><a href