(912, 171, 'Car Protection and Enrichment Package - by Carnation', 5649, 1099, 'car-protection-and-enrichment-package-by-carnation.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>A combination pack to make your car feel like new inside out.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong> </strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Car Wash</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong> </strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Cleaning of the exterior and underbody of the vehicle with pressurized water and with application of Shampoo.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>                   </strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Wash your car regularly! Things like bugs, bird''s dropping, or limestone dripping damage the paint leaving permanent stains if not washed off in time.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">In winter time, the chrome wheels and other chrome trim parts could be damaged by corrosion if the vehicle is not washed after driving on the roads when the salt was used. When the car is clean, all the moisture dries up quickly, but when it''s dirty, the moisture accumulates in dirty areas causing corrosion.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">The pressure wash removes the dirt from difficult to reach areas that speed up the corrosion process. Pressure wash also cleans all the dirt from the windshield. The sand that left out on the windshield gets caught by the windshield wipers blades and scratches the windshield when the wipers are operating. </span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Clean the leaves and other debris from the areas below the windshield and the water channels under the hood and trunk is important, as the leaves block the water drains and collect the moisture, speeding up the corrosion process and causing a damp smell inside your car.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Interior Cleaning</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong> </strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Extensive cleaning of car''s interior including  seats,  dash,  roof,  mats etc to restore the overall clean and hyegnice interior feel.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong> </strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Car detailing is the performance of an extremely thorough cleaning, which not only improves the appearance of cars, but also helps to preserve the car, and thus, increases resale value.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">It involves interiors thoroughly vacuumed including boot, seats, carpets and upholstery shampooed rejuvenating pile and color.  Dashboard, fascias, ashtrays are cleaned and conditioned. </span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> Interior vinyl’s and leather are cleaned and conditioned to produce a durable, enriched appearance.. Interior windows are also cleaned and polished. Recommend for all cars for hygienic, clean interiors.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong> </strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Paint Protection Solution</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong> </strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Application of protective chemical coating to safeguard the exterior paint surface of car against natural elements.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong> </strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Car Paint protection is the performance of an extremely thorough cleaning, polishing and waxing of an automobile, to produce a show-quality level of detail. Besides improving the appearance of cars, detailing helps to preserve the car, and thus, increases its resale value.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Paint protection retains the new look of the car by providing a polymeric protective film coating, above the vehicle’s paint work, on the clear coat, which protects against regular automatic car wash scratches, fading of paint, bird droppings, UV rays, acid rain, retaining the gloss and shine.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Once you get paint protection, you won’t need to polish the car for at least one year.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Paint protection enhances shine and seals the natural paint finish by filling in the castellation in every painted and clear coat surface where dirt, grime and pollutants can collect. Once the protection is complete, no chemical residue or coating remains on the paint.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><a href="/carnation-faq.html" target="_blank">How to Avail Service</a>? </span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><a href="/carnation-hubs.html" target="_blank">Where to Avail this Service</a>?</span></div>\r\n<p>?</p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
