(964, 151, 'STP Oil Treatment 443 ml', 445, 195, 'stp-oil-treatment-443ml.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Fights friction to help protect against engine wear by providing a thicker cushion between moving engine parts.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">This high-viscosity formula is specially formulated to help fight metal-to-metal friction by providing a thicker cushion between moving engine parts.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Helps</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">    Protect against engine wear</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">    Reduce oil consumption</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">    Protect engine parts</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Usage Frequency</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Use every oil change.?</span></p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(965, 69, 'STP Engine Flush 450 ml', 420, 44, 'stp-engine-flush-450-ml.jpg', '<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">High-quality motor oils are also known to form acids due to combustion by-products, high temperatures and oxidation.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"> The grit and sludge-forming acid deposits in the crankcase even after you have drained the engine oil and replaced the filter.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">STP Engine Flush is specially formulated to rapidly dissolve harmful engine deposits and maintain efficient oil circulation throughout the entire engine, helping to protect vital engine wear surfaces throughout the flush.?</span>?</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"> It has anti-wear additives that help <strong>protect vital engine wear surfaces</strong> during cleaning.  STP engine flush, when added to the used motor oil prior to draining helps neutralise engine acids.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"> It <strong>loosens and removes sludge, varnish and gum</strong> deposits that ordinary draining may leave behind.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>About The Brand</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong><br /></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">STP is a line of automotive additives and lubricants manufactured by Armored AutoGroup. Based and headquartered in Oakland, California, USA, the company constantly innovates and tests out new automotive technologies to expand their product line. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">Considered a leader in automotive car, STP has been delivering performance products for over 50 years. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">With regular use of STP (Scientifically Treated Petroleum), you can give your car engine a longer and better life. ?<br /></span></p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
