(1076, 69, 'Hella-Premium Wiper Blade 14 inches (Pack of 1)', 149, 10, 'hella-premium-wiper-blade-14-pack-of-1.jpg', '<h3><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>Description</strong></span></h3>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">Legend:- D- Driver Side, P- Passenger Side, R- Rear Side.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">D:-Vitara/Versa, Bolero, Indica Old, Innova, Qualis, Passat, Jetta</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">P:-Fiesta, Fusion, Figo, Aveo, U-VA, Tavera, Captiva,Tucson, I-10, I-20, Santro, Verna, Alto, Versa,Ritz, Wagon R, Zen, Corolla, Innova, Qualis, Indigo, Indica Old, Passat, Jetta</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">R:-Pajero</span></p>\n<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"> </p>\n<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>Highlights</strong></span></p>\n<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">One Hella Premium Wiper Blade made from top quality nanotechnology graphite-coated rubber. Minimum friction, wear-resistant and environmental-friendly.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;"><br /></span></p>\n<h4><strong><span style="font-size:12pt;">Description</span></strong></h4>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">Driving in the rain is a norm in this country, and we want to ensure that you’re always prepared with quality wipers for safe journeys. Here’s what we pulled together for you:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li>\n<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><span style="font-size:12pt;">One Hella Premium Wiper Blade</span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><span style="font-size:12pt;">Choose from 12”, 14”, 16”, 17”, 18”, 19”, 20”, 21”, 22”, 24” and 26”</span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><span style="font-size:12pt;">Price ranges from Rs. 145/=</span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><span style="font-size:12pt;">Meets the stringent test standards of Japanese Industrial Standards (JIS) and So