(1077, 272, 'COIDO-6025 Car Vacuum Cleaner Wet and Dry', 949, 38, 'coido-6025-car-vacuum-cleaner-wet-and-dry.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Product parameters</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">1. Inspiratory flow: above 12mmH</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">2. Power Supply: 12V DC</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">3. Input power: 60-65W</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">4. Output power :45-50W</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">5. Accessories: Ischaemum straw</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">6..Power cable : 420cm</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Notes</strong></span><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">1.Filters must be installed when you use the car vacuum cleaner.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">2.Do not put the car vacuum cleaner under sunshine directly, or under the high temperature and high pressure areas.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">3.Do not use gasoline or highly volatile detergent to wipe the body of car vacuum cleaner</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">4.Do not take out the shell when the motor is working.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">5.This car vacuum cleaner is not a toy, do not let children play alone.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">6.This vacuum cleaner only can use on the standard vehicle 12V power supply.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Usage</strong></span><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">1.Put the car vacuum cleaning cigarette lighter plug into the car cigarette jack.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">2.Control the power switch button , ON position to use, OFF to stop using.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">3.Depending on the use of different occasions to replace the suction nozzle, 5m long cigarette lighter cable,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">It is enough to cover the interior of the vehicle when you use the car vacuum cleaner.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">4.Let the suction flat the ground to achieve better results.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">5.The power control button is in the front of the former shell of the car vacuum cleaner press</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">it down and removable shell, when you finished, cleaning pls open the front cover and clean the filter to</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">prolong life, clean the filter must be away from the eyes and ears.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">6.This product can not use for the combustion stuff such as the burning cigarette butts and so on.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">7.In the case of wet and dry vacuum cleaner,should be pay attention the water or wet materials,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">attention to water height of the front cover of the resistance (capacity), inhalation height must not exceed the amount of water resistance.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">(To be turned off to open the front cover and then poured liquid water or wet Replace before re-use)</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>cleaning method</strong></span><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Remove the dirty things and clean the filter bag method:</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">1.Take out the dirty things from the net bag, press the spring and turn the net bags to remove it,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">put your hand into the net bag to take out the filter bag and pour out the dirty things </span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">2.Cleaning filter bags:</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">A:Rushed filter bags</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">B:Shake the filter bag in the garbage bag jitter</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">C: Wipe with detergent and with a paper towel after washing, confirm whether the former to keep clean when you use it again.</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">3.re-install filter bag:</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Align the bottom of the filter bag mesh bag so that it fits together, resulting in spring together with the filter bags.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Cleaning of plastic parts:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Use a damp cloth with hot water and mild detergent, in order to avoid to destroy the plastic parts. Pls do not use other detergents which may contain chemical substances.</span></p>\r\n<p>?</p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(1078, 272, 'New Coido 6132 Car Vaccum Cleaner - Wet And Dry', 949, 44, 'new-coido-6132-car-vaccum-cleaner-wet-and-dry.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size:12pt;">Transparent removable front cover, equipped with special filters to facilitate regular cleaning.</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">With transparent water storage, volume 0.5KG, can be stored in liquid adsorption.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">With a dedicated corner of the adsorption of flat head, can absorb corner of dust, great suction.</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Use Directly from the car lighter socket.</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Pick up dust , water , wet and dry particles.</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Inspiratory Flow rate : more than 12mmHG.</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Complete with Convenient attachment and washable filter .</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Cervical Tool for hard-to-get area.</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Compact and Light Weight</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Washable filter is easy to clean , environmentally friendly &amp; cost saving.</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">Dimension: 36 x 8 x 12 cm.</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;"><strong>Item Included:</strong></span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">1 X Coido 6132 Vacuum Cleaner</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style="font-size:12pt;">1 x Cervical tool</span></p>\n<h1 class="western"> </h1>', '2016-05-27 16:35:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
