(1086, 275, 'Breathalyzer Keychain Car Gadget - Flashlight + Stopwatch(Digital)', 300, 10, 'breathalyzer-keychain-car-gadget-flashlight-stopwatchdigital.jpg', '<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Digital LCD Breath Keychain Alcohol Tester &amp; Timer With Flashlight</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Description:</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">This is a portable 3 in1 alcohol tester.Inspecting alcoholic thickness by testing user'' s exhalation.</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">It has three key functions: alcohol test, torch function and timer function.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Features:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Threaded by keychain in order to be more convenient carrying</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Quick response and resume capacity</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Flashlight torch function(Orange light)</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Colored LED display alcohol level</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Functions:</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Alcohol test</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Press and keep holding the "POWER" button about 10 seconds, the green LED will be lighted on.</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Indicating the tester has entered into testing status.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">After 10 seconds later, exhale pneuma into exhale pipe and look into the result as follows:</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">IF Green LED keeps lighting: Safety-under 0.02% BAC(Blood Alcohol Concentration) or 0.1mg/L BRAC</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">IF Yellow LED keeps lighting: Caution-under 0.02%-0.05% BAC(Blood Alcohol Concentration) or 0.1mg/L-0.25mg/L BRAC</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">IF Red &amp; Yellow  LED keeps lighting: Danger-over 0.05% BAC(Blood Alcohol Concentration) or 0.25mg/L BRAC</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Notice</strong>: Please make sure to keep holding the "POWER" button during test</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Timer function:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Two timing modes: Count-up, Count-down</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">To count-up timing: press the "START/STOP" button to start, repress the button to stop.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">To count-down timing: press the HR and MIN to set limiting hours and minutes in advance. </span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Press the "START/STOP" button to start, repress the button to stop. It can preset time between 1min to 19hrs 59mins.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">To reset timing: press the HR and MIN simultaneously.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Torch function:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Slide the "ON/OFF" foward, then the LED lighting up with orange light</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Power supply: 2pcs 1.5V AAA battery(NOT included)</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Dimension: 74*36*22mm</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Color: black</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">1. 3 test steps with LED indication of alcohol concertration</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">2. Quick response and resume</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">3. Clock &amp; Alarm</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">4. Real time &amp; Countdown timer</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">5. Material:ABS</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Use this alcohol breath tester to analyze Blood Alcohol Concentration (BAC) at anytime and anywhere. Special designed for drunk driving. </span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">LED display is easy for you to read! This alcohol breath tester with LED torch and keychain is easy for you to carry!</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Portable and convenient to carry on keychain.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Easy to use and quick response and resume :</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Press and hold the power button, red and yellow LEDs will light"</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Just exhale into the vent to get your BAC immediately.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">In about 20 seconds, the green LED will keep lighting for READY instead of red&amp; yellow LEDs. The unit enters into the testing status.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Promptly and conveniently design for measuring BAC.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">3 test step with LED indication :</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Safety: under 0.02% BAC (0.1 mg/l BRAC)</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Caution: 0.02%~0.05% BAC (0.10~0.25 mg/l BRAC)</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Danger: over 0.05% BAC (0.25 mg/l BRAC)</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Item Includes:</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">1 x Alcohol breath tester and timer with flashlight</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">1 x User manual </span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">1xKey chain</span><br />?</p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
