(1100, 165, 'Hella Rallye 1000 Series 55 Watt 12 V Black Magic Driving Lamp (HL IAM004 700) - Set of 2 pcs', 12796, 10, 'hella-rallye-1000-series-55-watt-12-v-black-magic-driving-lamp-hl-iam004-700.jpg', '<p>Details<br /><br />The Black Magic 1000 Driving Light is one of the chameleons in Hella’s driving light offering. Hella’s exclusive Black Optics™ Technology starts with a striking all-black look when the lamp is off...but flip the switch and you get a super bright, enhanced-focus driving beam. The Black Magic 1000 Driving Light’s styling brings a stealth look to high performance lighting!<br /><br />The Hella Black Magic 1000 Driving Light uses a halogen bulb that distributes its light with an aluminum vapor coated parabolic reflector mounted behind a large round lens (almost 7" in diameter). The lens is surrounded by a black decorative ring that is bonded to a high-impact black ABS housing. This results in a watertight, trendsetting auxiliary driving lamp assembly for upright single-stud pedestal mounting in the grill or on the bumper.<br /><br />Hella Black Magic 1000 Driving Light Kit includes:<br /><br />    (1) Black Magic Lamps (7.32" Dia. x 8.58" H x 3.47" D)<br />    (2) H2 12V55W Bulbs<br />    Rocker Switch<br />    Installation Parts<br />    Ready-to-Use Wiring System with In-Line Fuse for Added Circuit Protection<br />    Easy-to-Follow Instructions<br /><br /> <br />Hella Black Magic Driving Lights Kit - How It Works<br />Black Magic Light On<br />55w H2 Halogen: You get dual 55w H2 halogen bulbs for clean, clear, evenly-distributed light Black Magic Light Off<br />Black magic creates a striking all black look when the lamp is off. Flip the switch and you get a super bright, enhanced-focus driving beam.<br />Hella Black Magic Driving Lights Kit     Black Optics Technology<br />Black Optics Technology: creates a striking all black look when the lamp is off. Flip the switch and you get a super bright, enhanced-focus driving beam.<br /><br /><br />Additional Features<br /><br />Black Magic Light Off: Black magic creates a striking all black look when the lamp is off. Flip the switch and you get a super bright, enhanced-focus driving beam.<br /><br />Black Magic Light On: 55w H2 Halogen: You get dual 55w H2 halogen bulbs for clean, clear, evenly-distributed light<br /><br />Hella Black Magic Driving Lights Kit: Black Optics Technology: creates a striking all black look when the lamp is off. Flip the switch and you get a super bright, enhanced-focus driving beam.<br />Black Magic Installed: Awesome Driving Light Power: The Hella Black Magic Light Kit adds awesome driving light power to any vehicle<br />Black Magic Front Dimensions: Dimensions: 8 7/8"H x 7 3/8"W x 3 7/16"D</p>\r\n<p><br /><a href="http://www.myhellalights.com/index.php/download_file/-/view/655/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.myhellalights.com/files/9012/7480/0035/pdf_icon_25x25.jpg" alt="wrench.png" width="25" height="25" align="absMiddle" /></a><a title="Ralle 1000 Black Magic mounting instructions" href="http://www.myhellalights.com/index.php/download_file/-/view/654" target="_blank">Rallye 1000 Black Magic mounting instructions</a>??</p>', '2016-05-27 16:35:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
